org.ecoinformatics.seek.datasource

Class EcogridDataCacheItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.objectmanager.cache.CacheObject
      • org.kepler.objectmanager.cache.DataCacheObject
        • org.kepler.objectmanager.cache.BufferedDataCacheObject
          • org.ecoinformatics.seek.datasource.EcogridDataCacheItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, CacheObjectInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EcogridCompressedDataCacheItem, EcogridMetaDataCacheItem

    public class EcogridDataCacheItem
extends BufferedDataCacheObject
    This class is not as generic as the name may indicate. It is designed to get the metadata to determine where the data is stored and then does a Ecogrid "get" to the data.
